      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ebz to atgreeſohs es/ un\nBuſraudſiju wiſſas Ap-\nbehdiṇaſchanas/ kas no-\nteẻ appakſch Saules/ un redſi/\ntur bija Apbehdiṇato Afaras/\nn kam Eepreeziṇatajs ne bija/\nn winzo Apbehdiṇataji bija\nvarreni/ bet ſcheem Eepreeziṇa-\najs ne bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad flaweju es tohs Mir-\ncschus/ kas jaw bij nomirruſchi\nvatrak/ neka tohs Dshwue/ kas\nvehl dshwi irraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam wehl labbaki/ ne-\na teem abbeem/ kas wehl wiſſ\newaid/ kas wiſſat ne irr redſeje\nto ntfnu Darbu/ kas noteek ap-\npakſch Saules.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl apraudſiju es wiſſu\nDarbu/ un wiſſadu Tikunu/\nka tadeht weens Zilweks to ob-\ntru skausch/ ir tas irr Neleetiba\nun Dwchfeles-Mahrdinaſchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Gekkis taleek jawas\nRohkas/ un ehd tawn paschn\nMeetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weena Sanja pilna ar\nMeevu irr labbaka/ neka abbe-\njas Sanjas pilnas ar Gruhtu-\nmu un Sirde-Wahrgeſchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atkah atgreeſohs es/ un\nuſluhkoju weenu Neleetibu ap-\npakſch Saules.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weens irr un ne diwi/\nwinnam arri ne irr Dehls/ nedš\nBrahlis/ tomehr wiſſch ta strah-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "da/ ka Galla newaido/ un winna\nAzzis ne tohp ar Baggatibu pſ-\nditas. Kam tad? un kurram\nſtrahdaju es? un atrauju man-\nnai Dwchfelei to Labbumu? tas\nirr arridsan Neleetiba un tauns\nGruhtans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Diwi irr labbaki neka\nweens/ jo teem irr labba Alga\nno fawa Darba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo kad tee friht/ tad us-\nzelf tas weenajs fawu Draugu:\nBet waj tam weenam kad tas\nfriht/ jo ohtra newa/ kas winnu\nuszelt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad arridsan diwi kohta\ngult/ tad teem irr Gutums/ bet\nka warr weens fatilditces?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja kas to weenu pahr-\nwarretu/ tad tee diwi tam warr\nprettistahweht: Un weens trihs-\nkahrtigs Auklis ne tohp drihs fa-\nranſtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Labbaks irr weens nab-\nbags un gudrs Behrns/ neka\nweens wezz Kehniſsch/ kas Geſ-\nkis irr/ kas ne finna wairs Pa-\nmahzitcbann peeneint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo zits nahk no Zeetuma-\nNamina/ un tohp par Kehniſſu/\nun zits/ kas fawa Walstiibādsim-\nmis irr/ panihſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es eeraudſiju wiſſus Dsh-\nwus appakſch Saules staigajam\nar to ohtru Behrnu/ kas winna\nWeeta stahwehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſo to Zaſchu/ kas\nwinna Preckſcha bijufcht/ ne irr\nGals/ un tee/ kas wehl pehz\nbuhs/ ne preezafecs pahr winnu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
